The core purpose of creating this library is Roman to Urdu Transliteration using word list. The table for mapping is discussed in:

Ahmed, T. (2009). Roman to Urdu Transliteration using word list. Conference of Language and Technology, submitted

Further help was taken from following paper:

Tafseer Ahmed, Roman to Urdu Transliteration using word list

